 "name": "RPlog_Morning_Caf",
 "title": "Morning Caf",
 "summary": "At the fashionable Caspar Caff #23 in Plaxton, the Sith Presav Crestian stops for caf after a night of festivities, accompanied by the eccentric engineer-doctor Druze and the protocol droid V1C3. They are joined by Crestian's daughter Atsvara and the soft-spoken pilot Nara, and the group falls into wry, freewheeling banter about scallop pastries, Biscuit Baron's troubled launch, Jolly Meal toys, and Druze's various professions. Druze fusses over Nara's health with a pen-light, the droid trades quips in mock-Jawaese, and the relaxed gathering enjoys an easy morning together before parting on friendly terms.",
